nodes.long_description:
In the near future the Earth is ruined and undead corpses
is the only thing walking the streets that were populated by
living humans in the past. 
Survive in a post-apocalyptic Earth and destroy 
as many undead as you can before they take you down!!

------Mutated Virus has the best graphics you have ever seen on Quest-----
------Official support on Quest 2 (72FPS ​ 80 FPS 90 FPS)--------

- ''Mutated Virus'' exploits to the fullest the hardware capabilities of the Oculus Quest. 
The experience from the game mechanics and graphics feels 
just like playing the game in Oculus Rift. 
A full PC-VR experience compacted into the Oculus Quest platform! 

- Smooth motion and framerate
- Official support on Quest 2 (72FPS ​ 80 FPS 90 FPS)
- Free Movement
- 14 Weapons
- 3 Maps
- 16 Zombies
- Wordwide Leaderboards
- Survival mode
- Latest Gen Graphics and FX (4 GEN) 
- Snap turning
- Movable lights
- Dual Weapons

nodes.change_log:
-- Major Update Released Version 4.3 
Thank you for your continued support of Mutated Virus! We're thrilled to announce the release of our major Update Version 4.3! This update brings a wealth of significant changes that will fundamentally enhance the visual experience, performance, and gameplay.
Check out the key improvements:
New Enemies 
The game now features an upgraded physics system
Enjoy Near-4K Visuals!** Experience incredible clarity on all devices! We've boosted the resolution by 63%, from 90% to 153%, bringing the visuals closer to 4K resolution. (All devices)
Real Dynamic Shadows:** Witness a world with true depth! Our new Real Dynamic Shadows system allows for realistic shadow casting and interaction based on light sources and objects in real-time. (Quest 3, Quest 3S, and future devices)
Vibrant Foliage:** The world feels more alive than ever! We've added detailed Foliage that visually enriches the environments. (Quest 3, Quest 3S, and future devices)
Dynamic Resolution:** For smoother performance across all devices, we've integrated Dynamic Resolution that adjusts automatically. (All devices)
4K AI-Enhanced Textures:** Visual fidelity reaches a new level! The vast majority of textures have been upgraded to stunning 4K resolution using cutting-edge AI technology. (All devices)
Smarter Enemies:** Battles become more engaging and challenging! The upgraded Enemy AI system makes opponents smarter and more strategic. (All devices)
Realistic Decals:** See the true impact of combat! We've added bullet and blood decals for a more realistic experience. (All devices)
Dynamic Foveated Rendering:** Focus on the detail! Dynamic Foveated Rendering optimizes clarity in your focal point while maintaining performance. (All devices)
Eye Tracking Support:** Immerse yourself even further! We've added Eye Tracking support for compatible devices. (Quest Pro and future devices)
Improved FX:** The action is more impressive than ever! We've revamped the visual effects for greater detail and impact. (All devices)
Numerous Gameplay Changes:** Get ready for a refreshed gameplay experience with a multitude of adjustments and improvements. (All devices)
New 120 FPS Option:** Enjoy incredibly smooth gameplay! We've added an option for 120 frames per second for those with compatible displays. (Quest 3, Quest 3S, and future devices)
New Anti-aliasing Options System:** Customize your visual smoothness to your liking! We've implemented a new Anti-aliasing options system. (Quest 4+)
*Enjoy a more stable and polished game experience thanks to numerous bug fixes
-- We hope you enjoy this major update for Mutated Virus! We look forward to hearing your feedback and continuing to improve the game together*Enjoy a more stable and polished game experience thanks to numerous bug fixes
